content: The parade goes past a soaring Gothic cathedral built by Irish immigrants and named for St. Patrick, who is the patron saint of both Ireland and New York City.
translations: ita:La parata passa davanti a una svettante cattedrale gotica costruita da immigrati irlandesi e intitolata a San Patrizio,
